synopsis.text: Legend tells of a hidden Sea Temple created by the Water People, holding the powerful Sea Crown treasure. Ash and friends meet Lizabeth, a Water People descendant, and Jackie, a Pok√©mon Ranger secretly protecting a Manaphy Egg that can locate the temple. The villainous Phantom, a pirate seeking world domination, knows Manaphy is the key to finding and claiming the Sea Crown. He has stolen the Manaphy Egg but Jackie interferes with his plans. Now Lizabeth and Ash must help Jackie protect the Egg and return Manaphy home safely. Along the way, Manaphy bonds closely with May. Phantom lurks, determined to capture Manaphy, solve the mystery of the moving Sea Temple, and seize the Crown to rule the seas!
